{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/settags:"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setTags:","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"NSDictionary","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSDictionary"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"tags","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Dictionary of tag names and values to set for the current device"}]}],"name":"tags"}]},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Tags are key-value pairs that enable targeted push notifications based on user attributes"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"and behavior. Use tags to segment your audience and send personalized messages to specific"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"user groups.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","text":"Supported Tag Types","anchor":"Supported-Tag-Types","level":2},{"rows":[[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Type","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Example","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Description"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"String"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"\"city\": \"New York\"","type":"codeVoice"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Text values","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Integer"}]}],[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"\"age\": 25","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Numeric values"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Boolean","type":"text"}]}],[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"\"isPremium\": true","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"True\/false values","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"List"}]}],[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"\"interests\": [\"sports\", \"music\"]","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Arrays of strings"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Date","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"\"lastPurchase\": Date()","type":"codeVoice"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"NSDate objects"}]}]]],"type":"table","header":"row"},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Example","anchor":"Example"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Update user profile tags after account changes:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["class UserProfileManager {","","    func updateUserTags(for user: User) {","        var tags: [String: Any] = [","            \"user_id\": user.id,","            \"email_verified\": user.isEmailVerified,","            \"account_type\": user.accountType.rawValue,","            \"signup_date\": user.createdAt,","            \"app_version\": Bundle.main.appVersion","        ]","","        \/\/ Add subscription info if premium","        if let subscription = user.subscription {","            tags[\"subscription_tier\"] = subscription.tier.rawValue","            tags[\"subscription_expiry\"] = subscription.expiryDate","            tags[\"is_premium\"] = true","        } else {","            tags[\"is_premium\"] = false","        }","","        \/\/ Add user preferences","        if !user.interests.isEmpty {","            tags[\"interests\"] = user.interests","        }","","        \/\/ Add location if available","        if let location = user.location {","            tags[\"country\"] = location.country","            tags[\"city\"] = location.city","            tags[\"timezone\"] = location.timezone","        }","","        Pushwoosh.configure.setTags(tags)","        Logger.debug(\"User tags updated: \\(tags.keys.joined(separator: \", \"))\")","    }","","    func trackPurchase(product: Product, amount: Decimal) {","        Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","            \"last_purchase_date\": Date(),","            \"last_purchase_amount\": NSDecimalNumber(decimal: amount),","            \"last_purchase_category\": product.category,","            \"total_purchases\": incrementTag(\"total_purchases\")","        ])","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing"}],"kind":"content"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Sets user tags for device segmentation.","type":"text"}],"metadata":{"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setTags:","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setTags:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"setTags:","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setTags:","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Type Method","symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setTags:"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"sections":[],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"fragments":[{"text":"PWConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","title":"PWConfiguration","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","role":"symbol"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"type":"topic","role":"collection","kind":"symbol","title":"PushwooshCore","abstract":[{"text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/setTags:":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setTags:","type":"topic","role":"symbol","title":"setTags:","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setTags:"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setTags:","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets user tags for device segmentation."}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/settags:"}}}